com.adidas.sensors.api

Annotation Type SensorServiceState


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface SensorServiceState
    Sensor service states

    • Field Detail

      • STATE_UNKNOWN

        public static final int STATE_UNKNOWN
        The service has not yet been discovered and it's state is unknown.

      • STATE_NOT_AVAILABLE

        public static final int STATE_NOT_AVAILABLE
        The sensor does not implement this service.

      • STATE_READY

        public static final int STATE_READY
        The sensor seems to be connected and the gatt services have been discovered.

      • STATE_DISCONNECTED

        public static final int STATE_DISCONNECTED
        The sensor is disconnected.
